Step by Step Instructions to reproduce similar results 9


This Step by Step Instructions will help you to create similar Dashboard we see below.

Dashboard



 Download the file

Click on the link above  to download SQL files

Steps

1.      Check the SQL query and Execute

2.      You will see COMPLETE result as below



1.      Open Power BI desktop &   Click on get data

2.      Select SQL Server



1.      Browse to the location of the New York Database and select Airbnb Table from the database

2.      Click on transform to transform the data as required. In this stage we clean the data, check the data type of the column and replace Null value (if we are required to do so).






3.      Click on Close and Apply to apply the steps taken


  Finally, the table is loaded into the Power Bi Desktop
